'''喬治·歐文·「桑尼」·珀杜三世'''（{{lang-en|George Ervin "Sonny" Perdue III}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.georgiaencyclopedia.org/nge/Article.jsp?id=h-2801 |title=Inscoe, John C., [[New_Georgia_Encyclopedia|New Georgia Encyclopedia]] entry on Sonny Perdue, [[University_of_Georgia|University of Georgia]], 2/6/2004 |accessdate=2017-01-21 |archive-date=2013-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130201015251/http://www.georgiaencyclopedia.org/nge/Article.jsp?id=h-2801 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{bd|1946年|12月20日}}），是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2014/05/meet-david-perdue-he-might-be-georgias-next-senator/371308/ |title=Meet David Perdue—He Might Be Georgia's Next Senator |accessdate=2016-01-04 |archive-date=2015-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221143810/http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2014/05/meet-david-perdue-he-might-be-georgias-next-senator/371308/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2003年至2011年期間，桑尼·珀杜擔任第81任[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]州長職務。珀杜是喬治亞州自[[重建時期|重建時期]]以來首位共和黨州長。他於2017年4月24日獲參議院確認[[美國農業部長|美國農業部長]]任命<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.senate.gov/legislative/LIS/roll_call_lists/roll_call_vote_cfm.cfm?congress=115&session=1&vote=00112 |title=U.S. Senate: U.S. Senate Roll Call Votes 115th Congress - 1st Session |publisher=Senate.gov |date= |accessdate=2017-06-13 |archive-date=2018-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709155002/https://www.senate.gov/legislative/LIS/roll_call_lists/roll_call_vote_cfm.cfm?congress=115&session=1&vote=00112 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

